CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: New Era Helium, Inc. is an exploration and production company that sources helium produced in association with the production of natural gas reserves in North America. The Company currently owns and operates over 137,000 acres in Southeast New Mexico and has over 1.5 billion cubic feet of proved and probable helium reserves.
